The file `eff_large_wordlist.txt` is the EFF Large Wordlist for passphrases,
created by Joseph Bonneau and the Electronic Frontier Foundation (2016).

Source: https://www.eff.org/dice
Licensed under Creative Commons Attribution 3.0 (CC BY 3.0):
https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/

It is used verbatim as the word source for the passphrase generator. Only the
plain words are retained (the original dice-roll numbers are omitted).
